ar lajel ipwassnen.
Nseyya. Amarezg n Wid Ipseyyin!
Assen, a nnger inekkaôen!
Day ur nerra ara tamurt d ayen ijemâen
wid idren, akked wid immuten.
Nerra degs idurar âaooôen. S waman iéidanen, Nesswa kwen.
Assen, a nnger inekkaôen!
